If you are a vegetarian, or like interesting food, avoid this place at all costs.  You may be tempted to meet someone for lunch--  business purposes.  dont do it.  find another place downtown.   Its not worth the loss of $10.  when I went...the service was  slow, the atmosphere was stiffingly stuffy, and my salad was basically iceberg and some fruit.

